      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "It is not a lexical construct. It is syntax. Semantically it is redundant. It is not &#39;required by the compiler&#39;. The part about space/time is just drivel. None of this nonsense answers the question that was asked. Don&#39;t use code formatting for text that isn&#39;t code."
